      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2022-01-13</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2022-06-24T15:53:51Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Disaster Resiliency Planning Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Office of Management and Budget to establish guidance that requires federal agencies to incorporate natural disaster resilience into asset management and investment decisions. Specifically, the guidance must direct each agency to incorporate assessments of natural disaster risk information conducted by the agency, such as from vulnerability and other risk assessments, into asset management and investment decisions. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
